<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.839282>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Female anterior ends of several species of Merliniidae from Iran: A. Amplimerlinius uramanatiensis; B. A. macrurus; C. Paramerlinius neohexagrammus; D. A. paraglobigerus; E – G. A. globigerus; H. Nagelus obscurus; I & J. Merlinius brevidens; K. M. microdorus; L & M. M. nanus; N. M. indicus. All scale-bars = 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/839282/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

